{
  "design_notes": "Expert-level hard chart with distinct structural phases. Intro relies on simple syncopation and light holds on vocal cues. The first verse builds the physical groove with steady quarter/eighth patterns before the break. Breakdowns use longer vocal-anchored holds to give the player a physical rest before high-energy drops. The second half ramps up the kinetic demands using zigzag streams, crossover-tolerable turns, and accents mapping to high-pitched synth highlights. Gaps have been strictly managed below 4 seconds to maintain a continuous, engaging physical loop.",
